      "writtenOn": "2021-03-16T19:11:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ok, I saw that preApply takes a drawBounds and I wasn\u0027t sure if that had any effect on the result.\n\nShould drawPaint call preApply with the renderTarget bounds? Or with some really large bounds? What happens if the clip is a round rect clipped by the drawBounds?",
