      "writtenOn": "2021-03-16T19:20:56Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I guess I\u0027m not understanding what code paths change with dmsaa that would make us miss attemptQuadOptimization. Are we planning to have drawRect, or drawImage go through path rendering and never hit GrSDC::drawFilledQuad or drawTexturedQuad?",
