      "writtenOn": "2021-03-16T20:20:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think we should reroute to GrFillRRectOp within GrSDC. That way we don\u0027t have to worry about rect draws that don\u0027t go through SkGpuDevice.",
      "parentUuid": "c272cd8a_b991e3a1",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 335,
        "startChar": 4,
        "endLine": 337,
